Rockaway Parkway, north from Conklin Avenue, showing a W. P. A. highway project. In the background is the tower of the fire house of Engine No. 257, at Farragut Road. View 2 is in the same direction from Glenwood Road; view 3 shows the bend in the Parkway, between Farragut Road and Foster Avenue. At this point Rockaway Parkway ends and Rockaway Avenue begins.
